&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is 3)&lt;strong&gt; (a) - (iv), (b) - (i), (c) - (ii), (d) - (iii).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(a) Something that will solve all the problems - (iv) &lt;strong&gt;Panacea&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;Panacea&amp;quot; is a term that refers to a solution or remedy for all difficulties or diseases.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(b) Existing from the beginning of the world - (i) &lt;strong&gt;Primordial&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;Primordial&amp;quot; means existing at or from the beginning of time; primeval.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(c) Pain in a muscle - (ii) &lt;strong&gt;Myalgia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;Myalgia&amp;quot; refers to muscle pain and is a term used to describe muscle aches and pain, which can involve ligaments, tendons, and fascia, the soft tissues that connect muscles, bones, and organs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(d) Person who hates other people - (iii) &lt;strong&gt;Misanthrope&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A &amp;quot;misanthrope&amp;quot; is a person who dislikes humankind and avoids human society.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;quaint&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

