&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;quaint&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is an&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adjective&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and its meaning is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;attractive because of being unusual and especially old-fashioned&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

